+@captain
+Feature: Error handling improvements
+
+  Scenario: Invalid tide data format
+    Given the tide table contains invalid date format
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "2026-07-12T05:00:00Z"
+    Then the prediction fails with a descriptive error about invalid data
+
+  Scenario: Missing required fields in tide data
+    Given the tide table with missing time fields
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "2026-07-12T05:00:00Z"
+    Then the prediction fails with a descriptive error about missing fields
+
+  Scenario: Invalid after parameter format
+    Given the tide table for Fundy Cove
+    When I ask for the next high tide after "invalid-date-format"
+    Then the prediction fails with a descriptive error about invalid input
